@miscparty

- @allow_banning: Allow Banning Unconstitutional Parties
- @ban_kpd: Ban KPD
- @unban_kpd: Unban KPD
- @ban_nsdap: Ban NSDAP
- @unban_nsdap: Unban NSDAP
- @form_sapd: Form SAPD (Requires High Internal Dissent)
- @returnsandbox: Return To Sandbox Menu

@allow_banning
view-if: constitutional_protection == 0
go-to: miscparty
on-arrival: {!
Q.constitutional_protection = 1;
!}

Allowed banning unconstitutional parties.

@ban_kpd
go-to: miscparty
view-if: kpd_banned == 0 and constitutional_protection == 1
on-arrival: {!
Q.kpd_banned = 1;
!}

Banned the KPD.

@unban_kpd
go-to: miscparty
view-if: kpd_banned != 0 and constitutional_protection == 1
on-arrival: {!
Q.kpd_banned = 0;
!}

Unbanned the KPD.

@ban_nsdap
go-to: miscparty
view-if: nsdap_banned == 0 and constitutional_protection == 1
on-arrival: {!
Q.nsdap_banned = 1;
!}

Banned the NSDAP.

@unban_nsdap
go-to: miscparty
view-if: nsdap_banned != 0 and constitutional_protection == 1
on-arrival: {!
Q.nsdap_banned = 0;
!}

Unbanned the NSDAP.

@form_sapd
go-to: miscparty
view-if: sapd_formed == 0
on-arrival: {!
Q.sapd_formed = 1;
!}

Formed the SAPD.

