- @spd_supportraise: Raise SPD Support
- @spd_supportlower: Lower SPD Support
- @sapd_supportraise: Raise SAPD Support
- @sapd_supportlower: Lower SAPD Support
- @center_supportraise: Raise Center Support
- @center_supportlower: Lower Center Support
- @kpd_supportraise: Raise KPD Support
- @kpd_supportlower: Lower KPD Support
- @ddp_supportraise: Raise DDP/DStP Support
- @ddp_supportlower: Lower DDP/DStP Support
- @dvp_supportraise: Raise DVP Support
- @dvp_supportlower: Lower DVP Support
- @dnvp_supportraise: Raise DNVP Support
- @dnvp_supportlower: Lower DNVP Support
- @nsdap_supportraise: Raise NSDAP Support
- @nsdap_supportlower: Lower NSDAP Support
- @other_supportraise: Raise Other Support
- @other_supportlower: Lower Other Support
- @returnsandbox: Return To Sandbox Menu

@returnpartysupport
go-to: editpartysupport

@spd_supportraise
go-to: editpartysupport
on-arrival: {!
Q.workers_spd += 20;
Q.old_middle_spd += 20;
Q.new_middle_spd += 20;
Q.rural_spd += 20;
Q.unemployed_spd += 20;
Q.catholics_spd += 20;
!}

Raised support for SPD.

@spd_supportlower
go-to: editpartysupport
on-arrival: {!
Q.workers_spd -= 20;
Q.old_middle_spd -= 20;
Q.new_middle_spd -= 20;
Q.rural_spd -= 20;
Q.unemployed_spd -= 20;
Q.catholics_spd -= 20;
!}

Lowered support for SPD.

@sapd_supportraise
view-if: sapd_formed == 1
go-to: editpartysupport
on-arrival: {!
Q.workers_sapd += 20;
Q.old_middle_sapd += 20;
Q.new_middle_sapd += 20;
Q.rural_sapd += 20;
Q.unemployed_sapd += 20;
Q.catholics_sapd += 20;
!}

Raised support for SAPD.

@sapd_supportlower
view-if: sapd_formed == 1
go-to: editpartysupport
on-arrival: {!
Q.workers_sapd -= 20;
Q.old_middle_sapd -= 20;
Q.new_middle_sapd -= 20;
Q.rural_sapd -= 20;
Q.unemployed_sapd -= 20;
Q.catholics_sapd -= 20;
!}

Lowered support for SAPD.

